'''白魔龍'''（[[屬名|屬名]]：''Tsaagan''，意為「白色」）是一[[屬|屬]][[肉食性|肉食性]]的[[馳龍科|馳龍科]][[獸腳亞目|獸腳亞目]][[恐龍|恐龍]]，生存在[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]晚期，發現於[[蒙古|蒙古]]的{{link-en|牙道黑達組|Djadokhta Formation}}。

==發現及命名==
正模標本發現於1996年，最初被鑑定為[[伶盜龍|伶盜龍]]的標本。但1998年5月的CT掃描證實這是一個新物種。2006年12月，{{link-en|馬克·諾瑞爾|Mark Norell}}、詹姆斯·克拉克（James Clark）、亞倫·透納（Alan Turner）、彼得·馬克維奇（Peter Makovicky）、{{link-en|瑞欽·巴思缽|Rinchen Barsbold}}和提摩西·洛威（Timothy Rowe）敘述、命名了[[模式種|模式種]]，種名''Tsaagan mangas''轉寫自[[蒙古文|蒙古文]]的「цагаан мангас」，意即白色的怪獸，應將整個讀作一詞彙，使屬名來修飾[[種加詞|種加詞]]。<ref name="norelletal06">{{cite journal | last1 = Norell | first1 = M.A. | last2 = Clark | first2 = J.M. | last3 = Turner | first3 = A.H. | last4 = Makovicky | first4 = P.J. | last5 = Barsbold | first5 = R. | last6 = Rowe | first6 = T. | year = 2006 | title = A new dromaeosaurid theropod from Ukhaa Tolgod (Ömnögov, Mongolia) | journal = American Museum Novitates | volume = 3545 | pages = 1–51 | doi=10.1206/0003-0082(2006)3545[1:ANDTFU]2.0.CO;2| hdl = 2246/5823 }}</ref>

[[正模標本|正模標本]]'''IGM 100/1015'''是目前唯一已知的化石，發現於[[南戈壁省|南戈壁省]]Xanadu附近的牙道黑達組地層，年代可追溯至[[坎潘階|坎潘階]]，約7500萬年前。是一個保存良好的頭骨與一系列10節頸椎，以及一塊破損的左肩胛骨，屬於一隻成年個體。<ref name="norelletal06"/>

==敘述==
白魔龍是中等體型的馳龍科。2010年{{link-en|葛瑞格利·保羅|Gregory S. Paul}}估計身長2公尺及體重15公斤。<ref>Paul, G.S., 2010, ''The Princeton Field Guide to Dinosaurs'', Princeton University Press p. 137</ref>頭骨外觀大致類似伶盜龍，但在許多細節上有所不同：如頂部更結實平滑。[[自衍徵|自衍徵]]包含：頭骨後部的基枕突（paroccipital processes）與基翼骨（basipterygoids）長；[[顴骨|顴骨]]接觸[[鱗狀骨|鱗狀骨]]。<ref name="norelletal06"/>

==分類==
白魔龍屬於馳龍科。最初諾瑞爾等人的[[支序分類學|支序分類學]]分析指出牠的確切位置屬於[[伶盜龍亞科|伶盜龍亞科]]。<ref name="norelletal06"/>一份2010年的分析顯示牠與[[臨河盜龍|臨河盜龍]]近緣。<ref name="xuhoneetal2010">{{Cite journal|authors=[[徐星_(古生物學家)|Xu, X.]], Choinere, J., Pittman, M., Tan, Q., Xiao, D., Li, Z., Tan, L., Clark, J., Norell, M., Hone, D.W.E. and Sullivan, C.|date=19 March 2010|url=http://mapress.com/zootaxa/2010/f/z02403p009f.pdf|title=A new dromaeosaurid (Dinosauria: Theropoda) from the Upper Cretaceous Wulansuhai Formation of Inner Mongolia, China|journal=[[Zootaxa|Zootaxa]]|issue=2403|pages=1–9|access-date=2010-03-19|archive-date=2012-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313032955/http://eprints.ucl.ac.uk/19175/1/19175.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>後續森特（2011）、透納，馬克維奇和諾瑞爾（2012）爭辯道精美臨河盜龍其實是白魔龍的[[次異名|次異名]]。<ref name=Senter2011>{{cite journal | last = Senter | first = Phil | year = 2011 | title = Using creation science to demonstrate evolution 2: morphological continuity within Dinosauria (supporting information) | doi = 10.1111/j.1420-9101.2011.02349.x | journal = Journal of Evolutionary Biology | volume = 24 | issue = 10 | pages = 2197–2216 | pmid = 21726330 | url = https://digitalcommons.uncfsu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1005&context=bio_wp | access-date = 2021-02-25 | archive-date = 2018-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180721165949/https://digitalcommons.uncfsu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1005&context=bio_wp | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=TurneretalBAMNH>{{cite journal | author = Alan Hamilton Turner, Peter J. Makovicky and Mark Norell | year = 2012 | title = A review of dromaeosaurid systematics and paravian phylogeny | journal = Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History | volume = 371 | pages = 1–206 | doi=10.1206/748.1| hdl = 2246/6352 }}</ref>徐，皮特曼等人（2015）透過提出臨河盜龍現有和新發現的解剖細節來反駁異名的假設。<ref name="Xu Xing, Michael Pittman, Corwin Sullivan, Jonah N. Choiniere, Qing Wei Tan, James M. Clark, Mark A. Norell, Wang Shuo">{{cite journal |author1=Xu Xing |author2=Michael Pittman |author3=Corwin Sullivan |author4=Jonah N. Choiniere |author5=Qing Wei Tan |author6=James M. Clark |author7=Mark A. Norell |author8=Wang Shuo |year=2015 |title=The taxonomic status of the Late Cretaceous dromaeosaurid ''Linheraptor exquisitus'' and its implications for dromaeosaurid systematics |journal=Vertebrata PalAsiatica |volume=53 |issue=1 |pages=29–62 |url=http://www.ivpp.cas.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/201501/t20150112_4297277.html |access-date=2021-02-25 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517135917/http://www.ivpp.cas.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/201501/t20150112_4297277.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

